; scenes/fx/ExplosionSmall.tscn
; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; Small one-shot explosion VFX for basic enemies and turret deaths.
; Plays 6-frame "explode" animation at 12 fps then QueueFree()s itself.
; Camera shake: 0.25 s, ±6 px magnitude.
; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
